{"tid":1116234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好怕自己無力發夢","createTime":"2019-04-19T19:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T06:05:05.000Z","uid":15556,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75e4937485888ddee2b068e91cc979d93df04f12","tid":1116234,"uid":15556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:16:24.000Z","msg":"我想做一個紋身師<br />\n<br />\n於是幾年前開始儲畫，上年終於實踐拜師學藝。<br />\n<br />\n由於學費比較吃力又唔想屋企人擔心，<br />\n所以轉行做sales，收早放假就上鋪頭幫手學嘢。<br />\n前排師傅認為可以嘗試接客，<br />\n亦都好支持我轉做part time等自己有更多時間練習，間接地令我以為學滿師。<br />\n<br />\n奈何，原來全部只係自己既幻想，<br />\n學費要繼續俾，而接客嘅錢幾乎全歸鋪頭... <br />\n今日望出巴士窗外，<br />\n咁多年都無份安穩工作報答屋企，究竟仲好唔好咁任性尋找所謂嘅夢想？<br />\n無力感好重.. 啲眼淚更加停唔到...<br />\n<br />\n呻下，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc12c024675b8d09a270709b8bea63c8ce27835f","tid":1116234,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"自己買架生，<br />\nig吸客，<br />\nd畫同手工好，自然有客。<br />\n前題係你真係夠料。"},{"pid":"f7c116cc7db1180643cec8b0c8ef7f8335d253d9","tid":1116234,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T20:59:38.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都發緊音樂夢"},{"pid":"45d65a0febb5329e6c02b257dcc574ede8cab90a","tid":1116234,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"我都發緊藝術夢<br />\n<br />\n響香港搞依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}